Plot_ly

library(p8105.datasets)
data("ny_noaa") 
ny_noaa =
  ny_noaa %>%
  separate(date, into = c("year", "month", "day"), sep = "-") %>%
  mutate(year = as.integer(year),
         month = factor(month.name[as.integer(month)], levels = month.name),
         day = as.integer(day),
         prcp = prcp / 10,
         tmax = as.numeric(tmax) / 10,
         tmin = as.numeric(tmin) / 10)

Column

Minimum and Maximum temperature mapping snowfall in 2009

xlab = list(title = "Minimum temperature(째C)")
ylab = list(title = "Maximum temperature(째C)")

ny_noaa %>% 
  filter(year == 2009,
         !is.na(tmax),
         !is.na(tmin),
         !is.na(snow),
         snow > 0, snow < 100) %>%
  plot_ly(x = ~tmin, y = ~tmax, type = "scatter", mode = "markers",
          alpha = 0.5,
          color = ~snow) %>% 
  layout(xaxis = xlab, yaxis = ylab)

Column

Maximum temperature by month in 2009

xlab = list(title = "Month")
ylab = list(title = "Maximum temperature(째C)")

ny_noaa %>% 
  filter(year == 2009,
         !is.na(tmax),
         !is.na(tmin),
         !is.na(prcp)) %>% 
  plot_ly(x = ~month, y = ~tmax, color = ~month, type = "box") %>% 
  layout(xaxis = xlab, yaxis = ylab)

Precipitation by month in 2009

xlab = list(title = "Month")
ylab = list(title = "Precipitation(mm)")

ny_noaa %>% 
  filter(year == 2009,
         !is.na(tmax),
         !is.na(tmin),
         !is.na(prcp)) %>% 
  plot_ly(x = ~month, y = ~prcp, color = ~month, type = "bar") %>% 
  layout(xaxis = xlab, yaxis = ylab)
